🔭 Upcoming Features

🔐 Security & Forensics Additions
Keylogger (Optional Toggle) – Log keystrokes (forensics ya parental control type use).

USB History – Konse USB devices kab lage the (reg query se nikal sakte hain).

Security Logs Check – Failed logins, UAC bypass attempts, etc.

Hidden Processes Detector – Compare visible vs actual running processes.

Scheduled Tasks Listing – Suspicious autoruns ya persistent malware detect karne ke liye.

Detect Suspicious Network Connections – IP reputation check with VirusTotal API (optional online use).

⚙️ System Enhancement Ideas
CPU Temperature & Fan Speed – Especially useful for laptops or gaming setups.

GPU Usage and Temp – Real-time status for high-performance machines.

Running Processes Overview – Like Task Manager, but filtered output.

Windows License Status – Genuine or not.

List Installed Drivers – Driver issues ya missing detection ke liye.

BIOS Boot Order – BIOS-level info se forensics ko help mil sakta.

🌐 Network Intelligence Ideas
Local Network Device Scanner – Scan nearby IPs for active devices (arp + ping sweep).

DNS Configuration Check – DNS hijacking detect karne ke liye.

Wi-Fi SSID Sniffer – Visible nearby SSIDs and signal strength.

VPN Detection – Active VPN tunnel hai ya nahi, uska status.

🧰 Utility Features
Generate Report (HTML / TXT / JSON) – Save all recon in neat format.

Simple GUI with Buttons – Tkinter or PyQt for non-techy users.

Dark Mode CLI Output – Just for swag 😎
